         // ä¿®æ”¹å€¼ä¹Ÿéœ€è¦ .value\n```\n\n> ğŸ’¡ æ³¨æ„ï¼š`.value` åœ¨æ¨¡æ¿ä¸­ä¼šè‡ªåŠ¨è§£åŒ…ï¼Œæ— éœ€å†™ã€‚\n\n---\n\n### 3. `reactive()` â€”â€” åˆ›å»ºå“åº”å¼å¯¹è±¡\n\nç”¨äºåˆ›å»ºä¸€ä¸ªå“åº”å¼çš„å¯¹è±¡æˆ–å¼•ç”¨ç±»å‹ã€‚\n\n```js\nimport { reactive } from \'vue\'\n\nconst state = reactive({\n  name: \'Alice\',\n  age: 25\n})\n\n// ç›´æ¥è®¿é—®å’Œä¿®æ”¹\nstate.age++\n```\n\n> âš ï¸ ä¸è¦è§£æ„ `reactive` å¯¹è±¡ï¼Œå¦åˆ™ä¼šå¤±å»å“åº”æ€§ï¼š\n```js\nconst { name } = state // âŒ è§£æ„å name ä¸å†å“åº”\n```\n\n---\n\n### 4. `computed()` â€”â€” è®¡ç®—å±æ€§\n\nåˆ›å»ºä¸€ä¸ªä¾èµ–å…¶ä»–å“åº”å¼æ•°æ®çš„è®¡ç®—å€¼ã€‚\n\n```js\nimport { ref, computed } from \'vue\'\n\nconst count = ref(1)\nconst double = computed(() => count.value * 2)\n\nconsole.log(double.value) // 2\n```\n\næ”¯æŒ getter å’Œ setterï¼š\n```js\nconst fullName = computed({\n  get: () => firstName.value + \' \' + lastName.value,\n  set: (val) => {\n    [firstName.value, lastName.value] = val.split(\' \')\n  }\n})\n```\n\n---\n\n### 5. `watch()` å’Œ `watchEffect()` â€”â€” å“åº”å¼ç›‘å¬\n\n#### `watch`ï¼šç›‘å¬ç‰¹å®šæ•°æ®æº\n```js\nimport { ref, watch } from \'vue\'\n\nconst count = ref(0)\n\nwatch(count, (newVal, oldVal) => {\n  console.log(`count changed: ${oldVal} -> ${newVal}`)\n})\n```\n\nå¯ä»¥ç›‘å¬å¤šä¸ªæºï¼š\n```js\nwatch([count, name], ([c, n], [oldC, oldN]) => {\n  // ...\n})\n```\n\n#### `watchEffect`ï¼šç«‹å³æ‰§è¡Œå¹¶è‡ªåŠ¨è¿½è¸ªä¾èµ–\n```js\nwatchEffect(() => {\n  console.log(\'Current count:\', count.value)\n  // è‡ªåŠ¨ç›‘å¬ count.valueï¼Œä¸€æ—¦å˜åŒ–å°±é‡æ–°æ‰§è¡Œ\n})\n```\n\n> ğŸ” `watchEffect` æ›´ç®€æ´ï¼Œé€‚åˆå‰¯ä½œç”¨é€»è¾‘ï¼ˆå¦‚è¯·æ±‚æ•°æ®ï¼‰ã€‚\n\n---\n\n### 6. ç”Ÿå‘½å‘¨æœŸé’©å­\n\nåœ¨ `setup()` ä¸­ä½¿ç”¨å¸¦ `on` å‰ç¼€çš„å‡½æ•°æ³¨å†Œç”Ÿå‘½å‘¨æœŸé’©å­ï¼š\n\n```js\nimport {\n  onMounted,\n  onUpdated,\n  onUnmounted\n} from \'vue\'\n\nsetup() {\n  onMounted(() => {\n    console.log(\'Component mounted\')\n  })\n\n  onUpdated(() => {\n    console.log(\'Component updated\')\n  })\n\n  onUnmounted(() => {\n    console.log(\'Component unmounted\')\n  })\n}\n```\n\n| Options API       | Composition API         |\n|-------------------|--------------------------|\n| `mounted`         | `onMounted`              |\n| `updated`         | `onUpdated`              |\n| `beforeUnmount`   | `onBeforeUnmount`        |\n| `unmounted`       | `onUnmounted`            |\n\n---\n\n### 7. é€»è¾‘å¤ç”¨ï¼šè‡ªå®šä¹‰ Hookï¼ˆComposablesï¼‰\n\nè¿™æ˜¯ Composition API æœ€å¼ºå¤§çš„ç‰¹æ€§ä¹‹ä¸€ â€”â€” å°†å¯å¤ç”¨çš„é€»è¾‘å°è£…æˆå‡½æ•°ã€‚\n\n#### ç¤ºä¾‹ï¼šå°è£…ä¸€ä¸ªè®¡æ•°å™¨é€»è¾‘\n```js\n// composables/useCounter.js\nimport { ref } from \'vue\'\n\nexport function useCounter(initialValue = 0) {\n  const count = ref(initialValue)\n\n  const increment = () => count.value++\n  const decrement = () => count.value--\n  const reset = () => count.value = initialValue\n\n  return {\n    count,\n    increment,\n    decrement,\n    reset\n  }\n}\n```\n\nåœ¨ç»„ä»¶ä¸­ä½¿ç”¨ï¼š\n```vue\n<script setup>\nimport { useCounter } from \'@/composables/useCounter\'\n\nconst { count, increment } = useCounter(5)\n</script>\n\n<template>\n  <div>\n    <p>{{ count }}</p>\n    <button @click=\"increment\">+</button>\n  </div>\n</template>\n```\n\n> âœ… å¤šä¸ªç»„ä»¶å¯ä»¥å¤ç”¨åŒä¸€é€»è¾‘ï¼Œæ— å‘½åå†²çªï¼Œé€»è¾‘æ¸…æ™°ï¼\n\n---\n\n## ğŸ“š æ¨èå­¦ä¹ èµ„æºï¼ˆæ¥è‡ª CoderHub å¹³å°ï¼‰\n\nä¸ºäº†å¸®åŠ©ä½ æ›´å¥½åœ°æŒæ¡ Vue 3 Composition APIï¼Œæˆ‘ä¸ºä½ æ¨èä»¥ä¸‹ CoderHub ä¸Šçš„ä¼˜è´¨æ•™ç¨‹ï¼š\n\n1. **ã€ŠVue 3 å…¥é—¨åˆ°å®æˆ˜ã€‹**  \n   - ç³»ç»Ÿè®²è§£ Composition APIã€å“åº”å¼åŸç†ã€æ–°ç‰¹æ€§\n   - åŒ…å«å®æˆ˜é¡¹ç›®ï¼šTodoListã€ç”µå•†åå°ç­‰\n\n2. **ã€ŠComposition API æ·±åº¦è§£æã€‹**  \n   - æ·±å…¥å‰–æ `ref`ã€`reactive` å†…éƒ¨æœºåˆ¶\n   - å¯¹æ¯” Options API ä¸ Composition API çš„ä¼˜åŠ£\n\n3. **ã€Šæ‰“é€ å¯å¤ç”¨çš„ Composablesã€‹**  \n   - æ•™ä½ å¦‚ä½•ç¼–å†™é€šç”¨çš„è‡ªå®šä¹‰ Hook\n   - å®ç° `useFetch`ã€`useLocalStorage` ç­‰å®ç”¨å·¥å…·\n\n4. **ã€ŠVue 3 + TypeScript æœ€ä½³å®è·µã€‹**  \n   - ç»“åˆ TS ä½¿ç”¨ Composition APIï¼Œæå‡ç±»å‹å®‰å…¨\n\nğŸ‘‰ ä½ 